name: Elie MacDowell (Ao no Kiseki/Trails to Azure) LoRA
description:
Elie MacDowell from Ao no Kiseki/Trails to Azure. Trained on NAI.

Tested at 0.7-1.0 strength.

Trigger phrase is "Elie MacDowell".

  • Add "hairband, hair ribbon, blue ascot, red coat, white dress, black pantyhose, white boots" for her typical look.

  • The red pads/"wings" next to her legs are somewhat inconsistent because Elie's outfit really makes no sense. If you don't want to deal with this, replace "red coat" with "red jacket, belt".
